Source: ybaroj-sway-wm
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Maintainer: ybaroj <ybaroj@example.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.6.0

Package: ybaroj-sway-wm
Architecture: all
Depends: sway, waybar, greetd, wlgreet, tofi, foot, mako-notifier, swaylock, swayidle
Description: Custom Sway window manager meta-package with configurations
 This meta-package installs and configures the Sway tiling window manager
 along with related Wayland-based tools including Waybar (system bar),
 Greetd with wlgreet (display manager), Tofi (application launcher),
 Foot (terminal emulator), Mako (notification daemon), Swaylock (screen
 locker), and Swayidle (idle management daemon).
 .
 This package provides a complete, ready-to-use Sway desktop environment.
